{"tid":2036794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"5.27 最簡單 最有效 低風險玩法 同你講呀婆都做得","createTime":"2020-05-26T16:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T18:23:16.000Z","uid":218871,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"19589f77c2955a04f356a605614cd3f80fdf2f6c","tid":2036794,"uid":218871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:14:34.000Z","msg":"塞鐵： <br />\n人多固然重要，波子丶錫紙用下，多D搵下站務人員check 下月台下面。有人係車話你，唔好諗，即刻大聲問佢係咪攪事，唔好縮，你一出聲大把人幫你。<br />\n<br />\n塞車： <br />\n車手做到幾多得幾多，隧道口好多狗，自己決定，但係冇狗地方，試吓噴下巴士，試吓推野出馬路，一做即刻跑。唔好留。<br />\n<br />\n最後，你真係好驚，咩都唔好帶，black block，行下街，搵下frd。拉你都多舊魚，浪費下狗D時間幾好。金鐘好多朋友架。<br />\n<br />\n希望聽日可以好似5.24，有畫面，make 到noise，夠你哋，唔該曬！"},{"pid":"268a9e983f9c0f6dee26212d2c7aff8c4540750d","tid":2036794,"uid":218871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"992873082605a2d0b1843e834b599d0a164732a8","tid":2036794,"uid":218871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e9f3ce3ebbae20505332ad9378328652f26ee366","tid":2036794,"uid":218871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c4186ebb8e3eca3b1bdef05304f7fd0ca08e09bc","tid":2036794,"uid":218871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:17:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4258c23da0bed28eb8f480c087bff0aabcd08e5a","tid":2036794,"uid":218871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f67a06b25c995339a672d4478fb4e099fc259b01","tid":2036794,"uid":218871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7c90437c574bb0a5af3168c5d46ff31380d2872e","tid":2036794,"uid":218871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"065870a4f69d8b551ca87991bf1212c3bca0b307","tid":2036794,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"